#Describe the process to became a GROSCHATISTE

Step 1 : Pet or hug a living object (cat, dog, human, or any other thing you want)
Step 2 : Think about the universe and beyond, and decide that all of it can be, or could be a giant cat or any other living object
Step 3 : If you ve choosed cat on step 2 : you are now a GrosChatiste / If you choosed other animal or living object on step 2 , then you are now a GrosChatiste but from a specific branche related to the animal you choose
